 environmental policy or DABM (Dutch: Decreet houdende algemene bepalingen inzake milieubeleid/DABM), certain categories of establishments are subject to a periodic or one-off environmental audit. </p><p>This environmental audit as defined by the DBAM is an evaluation of the management, organisation and equipment of the establishment or activity concerned in terms of environmental protection. The environmental audit must be validated by a recognised environmental verifier. </p>"},"type":"Bewijs","themas":["MilieuEnergie"],"doelgroepen":["Burger","Onderneming","Organisatie"],"geografischToepassingsgebieden":["BE2"],"regelgevingTekst":{"nl-BE-x-generated-formal":"<ul><li><a href=\"https://eur-lex.europa.eu/eli/reg/2009/1221\">EMAS-verordening</a></li><li><a href=\"https://navigator.emis.vito.be/mijn-navigator?woId=308\">Decreet algemene bepalingen milieubeleid (DABM)</a></li><li><a href=\"https://navigator.emis.vito.be/mijn-navigator?woId=63105\">Omgevingsvergunningsdecreet</a></li><li><a href=\"https://omgeving.vlaanderen.be/vlarem\">VLAREM</a></li><li><a href=\"https://navigator.emis.vito.be/mijn-navigator?woId=38542&amp;woLang=nl\">Vlaams reglement inzake erkenningen met betrekking tot het leefmilieu (VLAREL)</a></li></ul>","en":"<ul><li><p>EMAS Regulation </p></li><li><p>Decree concerning general provisions relating to environmental policy (DABM) </p></li><li><p>Environmental Permit Decree </p></li><li><p>VLAREM </p></li><li><p>Flemish regulation on environmental recognitions (VLAREL) </p></li></ul>","nl":"<ul><li><a href=\"https://eur-lex.europa.eu/eli/reg/2009/1221\">EMAS-verordening</a></li><li><a href=\"https://navigator.emis.vito.be/mijn-navigator?woId=308\">Decreet algemene bepalingen milieubeleid (DABM)</a></li><li><a href=\"https://navigator.emis.vito.be/mijn-navigator?woId=63105\">Omgevingsvergunningsdecreet</a></li><li><a href=\"https://omgeving.vlaanderen.be/vlarem\">VLAREM</a></li><li><a href=\"https://navigator.emis.vito.be/mijn-navigator?woId=38542&a